$***********************$  * I OWE IT ALL TO JESUS... I OWE IT ALL TO JESUS... IF I AM EVER ANYTHING THEN, ALL THE PRAISE TO HIM I'LL BRING I OWE IT ALL TO JESUS... I OWE IT ALL TO JESUS... THIS SONG OF LOVE FROM DEEP WITHIN.... I OWE IT ALL TO HIM
$***********************$  1.If I've been used in some small way.... To help someone in need today.... If any good is found in me... It's just because of Calvary...
$***********************$  2.He touched my blinded heart and mind... And, now His precious ways I find.... Where He leads me I will go... So, many others need to know....

