$***********************$  1.My boat of life sails on a troubled sea Ever there's a wind in my sails, But my Heavenly Father, He watches over me When the breeze turns into a gale.
$***********************$  * I know the Master of the wind, I know the Maker of the rain, He can calm the storm And make the sun to shine again I know the Master of the wind.
$***********************$  2. Sometimes I soar like an eagle in the sky Among the peaks my soul can be found, An unexpected storm May drive me from the heights, It may bring me low, But it can never bring me down.

