$***********************$  1. Third exodus people, We are going back where we belong, Into the Land we had before the world was formed. The Lamb has redeemed us, by His Blood He paid the perfect price Claiming His own, He was the living Sacrifice.
$***********************$  * Come and feast from the Life-Tree, Feed on Its fruit and never be hungry, Be transformed into the image of the Word. For the Word in Its power is fully restored this very hour. We can easily drink, drink from the Spirit of God.
