$***********************$  1. Saints of all the ages that’s gone by, Longed to see this happ’ning in their time, But they died in faith anticipating for the day, Which is going on now, In this finishing hour.
$***********************$  2. Darkness holds the world in deadly grip, People’s hearts are in religious sleep, But there’s a holy and elected nation pure and right, For the harvest is ripe, Fields are ready and white.
