$***********************$  *We are redeemed and we are rejoicing, redeemed and singing to Him, Redeemed and giving Him honour, Giving glory to the Lamb, our King. He gave us full redemption, He sent the abundance of grace. So close is the hour of returning to our glorious Heavenly place.
$***********************$  1. God revealed it to us and we recognized our day and hour. It’s the harvest time, latter rain is coming in It’s power.  His storehouses are full of blessings from His Throne. We’re marching on, we’re going back, we’re going Home.
