$***********************$  *You are the center,  the Center of my life You’re the reason why I can live more abundantly Let there be  nothing, Nothing place before you So I can see you in plain view I want to do everything through Christ The center, The Center of my life
$***********************$  2. Whenever I begin my day with prayer You have never failed to meet me there And all the other things of life Just seem to work out right My heart are fixed on you and you alone Lord please come and rule upon this throne So that in this life of mine I can feel your presence all the time

