$***********************$ 1. Lord You chose me to overcome in this day You knew the tests that I will face in this evil age I'll leave those things behind and I'll run for the prize And press towards the mark of the high calling in Christ
$***********************$ * In the inner veil, Your promises I see Through your sacrifice on the cross Where You died to set me free I'm giving You my all that Your will be done in me Lord let me live my life in the inner veil Full submission Lord in the inner veil
$***********************$ 2. I'm dying every day to things I see in me In Your Word You promised, I'll have the victory For me to live is Christ and for me to die is gain Your promise I'll take no matter what the pain
$***********************$ 3. Lord I'm laying my all on the altar of sacrifice To be changed into Your image that I could reflect Your life On the threshing floor like Ruth in full obedience I will come Cover me with Your skirt that we two can become one

