$***********************$  1.We’ve seen uncovered all of satan’s scheme For God has made it plain, it is revealed! The keys have come back by the Word of the Hour The risen Lamb has conquered Over death, hell and the grave
$***********************$  2.Within religion hides the enemy But still we know the Bride won’t be deceived Partaking of the Word, we stand in faith; We’re chosen to withstand And overcome the pressures of the Age
