$***********************$ EN
$***********************$ 1. I will lift my voice to You Looking at Your holy temple. I believe You’ll give the victory And the enemies' camp I will trample. Saviour, open as I knock, Without You my heart is dying. Please, create in me Your wondrous work, Fill me up, Lord, I am crying Every day x3 I need You, Lord. 
$***********************$ 2. Turn my night into a day I don't want to grope in darkness And although sometimes I lose my way Satan’s lies will never part us. Lord, I raise my hand to You Lead me all the way to heaven Keep me focused on the Absolute, That’s the Word, which You have given. Every step ×3 I need You, Lord. 
$***********************$ 3. Jesus, I desire to be Just like You here every day. May Your character reflect in me, On my knees I humbly pray. May Your spirit and Your love Make my heart so soft and tender. Lead me by Your holy snow-white dove Lord, to You now I surrender. Hold me close, Hold me close to You. Hold me close, my Saviour God, to You.
$***********************$ 4. May I always be alert, And my eyes will not grow dim May I always know Your will and Word That my loved ones I could redeem. May all dirt just fall away When You’re testing me and shaking, Let me walk before You every day Clean and holy, Lord, I’m praying, Live in me, Live in me, oh Lord, Live in me, my Saviour, everyday.
$***********************$ 5. I won’t praise myself at all, Lord, to You I’ll give the glory. It’s Your mercy, Saviour, I’ll exalt Everyday on my life’s journey. You will raise me to the heights From the dark You will relieve me. Lord, I need You now, please, hold me tight, Cause You promised, You won’t leave me. Even now x3 I need You, Lord

